scrolllist_add_item Flags
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Gadget:	<ScrollList>
#Line
#Wrap off
Bits:	0 & 1	- Behave similarly to <OS_SpriteOP=>SWI:os_spriteop>.

	0 0	- Use WimpSprite Pool, with sprite_name as pointer to sprite name.
	0 1	- Pointer to sprite area, with sprite_name as pointer to sprite name.
	1 0	- Pointer to sprite area, with sprite_name as pointer to sprite.
#Line
To be used with <scrolllist_add_item>